      <rules>
        <rule id="4e87-7ad5-f7e3-7efc" name="Divination" hidden="false">
          <description>After both sides have deployed at the start of the game, the Eldar player my reposition D3 units in his army up to 6&quot; from its original position within the normal deploment zone. Additionally, when using reserves the Elday player may add +1 to a single reserve roll each turn.</description>
        </rule>
