    <selectionEntry id="8c5f-0df3-c1d0-3037" name="Star Serpent (VDR)" hidden="false" collective="false" import="true" type="upgrade">
      <comment>Based on Armourcast model / Upscaled Epic Model
Eldar Star Serpent Grav Tank
Type: Tank
Size: Normal
Armour: 14 14 10						(30 + 40 + 40 + 10 = 120 pts)
Fully Armoured
Speed: Fast								(+20 pts)
Characteristics: BS 3
Weapons: D-cannon 						(+30 pts)
Special Options: Skimmer, Transport 12	(20 + 12 = +22 pts)
Optional Upgrades: Codex: Eldar vehicle armory.
Total Points: 192 pts (Rounded to 190)</comment>
