    <selectionEntry id="d81b-5c7a-6af8-19af" name="Tempest (VDR)" hidden="false" collective="false" import="true" type="unit">
      <comment>Based on Armourcast model
Eldar Tempest Super Heavy Grav Tank
Type: Tank
Size: War Machine
Armour: 13 12 11				(20 + 20 + 20 + 20 = 80 pts)
Structure Points: 3				(+200 pts)
Fully Armoured
Speed: Agile					(+30 pts)
Characteristics: BS 4
Weapons: 
Twin-Linked Titan Killer Long-Barrel Mega Pulse Laser	(40 + 20 + 20 + 20 + 60 = +160 pts)
Twin-Linked Shuriken Cannon				(25 + 13 = +28 pts)
8x Shuriken Catapult					(4 x 8 = +32 pts)
Special Options: Eldar Fields (front, side), Skimmer, Souped-up Engine (50 + 20 = +70 pts)
Optional Upgrades: Codex: Eldar vehicle armory.
Total Points: 600pts</comment>
      <modifiers>
        <modifier type="set" field="hidden" value="true">
          <conditions>
            <condition field="selections" scope="force" value="1.0" percentValue="false" shared="true" includeChildSelections="true" includeChildForces="false" childId="eca8-ace3-d503-7923" type="equalTo"/>
          </conditions>
