                      <rules>
                        <rule id="9829-1fe8-7500-5dc7" name="Quickshot" hidden="false">
                          <description>Proficient at movement warefare, a Eldar Pirate can fire a Heavy Stubber while moving, albeit at the cost of accuracy. If a model equipped with a Heavy Stubber has moved, it may count the weapon as Assault 3 instead and their Ballisitic Skill as 2.</description>
                        </rule>
